        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="kpi-row cols-4">
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="kpi-label">New leads (30d)</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">38</div>
          <div class="kpi-meta"><span class="kpi-delta up">↑ 22%</span><span class="kpi-delta-label">vs last month</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="kpi-d360-flag"><span class="d360-pill">Predicted</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-label">Qualified (score 70+)</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">14</div>
          <div class="kpi-meta"><span class="kpi-delta-label">36.8% qualification rate</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="kpi-label">Conversion rate (90d)</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">18.4<span class="kpi-value-suffix">%</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-meta"><span class="kpi-delta up">↑ 3.1pt</span><span class="kpi-delta-label">peer avg: 14.2%</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="kpi-label">Avg response time</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">2.4<span class="kpi-value-suffix">hr</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-meta"><span class="kpi-delta up">↓ 1.8hr</span><span class="kpi-delta-label">target: under 4hr</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="d360-strip">
        <div class="d360-strip-mark"><div class="d360-strip-mark-inner"></div></div>
        <div class="d360-strip-text">
          <div class="d360-strip-eyebrow">Powered by Data 360</div>
          <div class="d360-strip-title">Lead scoring combines life-event triggers, online quoting behavior, and cross-carrier shopping signals to prioritize your outreach.</div>
          <div class="d360-strip-sub">Leads contacted within 2 hours of a life-event trigger convert at 3.2× the rate of leads contacted after 24 hours.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="d360-strip-stats">
          <div><div class="d360-strip-stat-num">5</div><div class="d360-strip-stat-label">Signals</div></div>
          <div><div class="d360-strip-stat-num">38</div><div class="d360-strip-stat-label">Scored</div></div>
          <div><div class="d360-strip-stat-num">live</div><div class="d360-strip-stat-label">Updated</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tabs">
        <div class="tab active">All leads <span class="tab-count">38</span></div>
        <div class="tab">Hot <span class="tab-count">14</span></div>
        <div class="tab">Warm <span class="tab-count">16</span></div>
        <div class="tab">Cold <span class="tab-count">8</span></div>
